# Financial Risk Operational Total Requirements Amount

## identifier
de8166

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of total operational risk requirements, as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Operational.TotalRequirements.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
